    {
      "num": 1,
      "geez": "ወእምድኅረ፡ ዝ፡ ወሀበኒ፡ ትእምርተ፡ ኵሎሙ፡ ኅቡኣት፡ በመጽሐፍ፡ እምኄውየ፡ ሄኖክ፡ ወምሳሌያተ፡ ዘተውህባ፡ ሎቱ፡ ወደመሮሙ፡ ሊተ፡ በነገረ፡ መጽሐፍ፡ ዘምሳሌ።",
      "translation": "And after that my grandfather Enoch gave me the teaching of all the secrets in the book in the Parables which had been given to him, and he put them together for me in the words of the book of the Parables.",
