    {
      "num": 3,
      "geez": "ወአውሥኦ፡ ካዕበ፡ ወይቤሎ፡ ቅዱስ፡ ሚካኤል፡ ለሩፋኤል፡ መኑ፡ ውእቱ፡ ዘኢያረኅርኅ፡ ልቦ፡ ዲቤሃ፡ ወኢይትሀወክ፡ ኵልያቲሁ፡ እምዛቲ፡ ቃል፡ ኵነኔ፡ ወፅአት፡ ዲቤሆሙ፡ እምኔሆሙ፡ ዘአውፅእዎሙ፡ ከመ፡ ዝ።",
      "translation": "And Michael answered again, and said to Raphael: ‘Who is he whose heart is not softened concerning it, and whose reins are not troubled by this word of judgement (that) has gone forth upon them because of those who have thus led them out?’",
